data.description: Indulge in the extraordinary views awaiting you from not one, but two balconies that unveil breathtaking Bay and City views! This recently remodeled 20th-floor unit at the Atrium boasts 2 generously sized bedrooms, 2 pristine baths, and the convenience of 2 designated parking spaces. Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by an expansive and truly open concept floorplan featuring raised ceilings and luxury vinyl plank flooring that extends gracefully throughout, creating a seamless and elegant ambiance. The living room features two glass sliding doors, infusing the interior with an abundance of natural light. A culinary masterpiece awaits in the custom gourmet kitchen, adorned with newer appliances (2022), modern light fixtures, and designer finishes that blend both style and functionality seamlessly. The oversized primary bedroom offers its own private balcony and unobstructed downtown views. The second bedroom offers versatility, serving as an ideal office space with its French doors that open gracefully to the living room. It also comes equipped with a Murphy bed, ensuring you can effortlessly transform the room to meet your needs. A dedicated laundry room, conveniently situated down the hallway, houses a full-sized washer and dryer for added convenience.  This unit has been upgraded with a state-of-the-art fire sprinkler system featuring concealed heads, providing added safety and peace of mind. Beyond your unit, The Atrium offers a wealth of amenities to elevate your lifestyle. With a 24/7 staffed front desk and security, you'll enjoy a heightened sense of security. The heated pool and spa, perched overlooking the bay, create an oasis of relaxation. Challenge your friends to a game of tennis on the rooftop courts, maintain your fitness regimen in the well-equipped fitness center, or unwind with a good book in the library. On-site management ensures that your needs are met promptly. This prime location on Bayshore Blvd offers unparalleled convenience. It's just a short stroll to Howard Avenue, where you can savor a wide array of culinary delights at restaurants, explore vibrant nightlife, and peruse the charming shops of Old Hyde Park. A brief drive takes you to downtown, Tampa General Hospital, Tampa International Airport, shopping malls, and Florida's top beaches on the Gulf Coast. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home. Call today to schedule a private showing and embark on a journey to luxurious living.
